{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be user-friendly and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>PodWave Network</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #007bff;\n            --secondary-color: #a0c8ff;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            --white: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--white);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--white);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-list {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item img {\n            width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--white);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--white);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>PodWave Network</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#podcasts\">Our Podcasts</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>Welcome to PodWave</h2>\n            <p>PodWave Network is a curated collection of engaging and informative podcasts covering a wide range of topics. We are dedicated to bringing you high-quality audio content that entertains, educates, and inspires. Join us on a journey through sound!</p>\n            <a href=\"#podcasts\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Shows</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"podcasts\">\n            <h2>Featured Podcasts</h2>\n            <div class=\"podcast-list\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/100/007bff/ffffff?text=P1\" alt=\"Podcast 1 Cover\">\n                    <h3>Tech Insights</h3>\n                    <p>Deep dives into the latest technology trends and innovations.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/100/007bff/ffffff?text=P2\" alt=\"Podcast 2 Cover\">\n                    <h3>History Uncovered</h3>\n                    <p>Exploring fascinating historical events and figures.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/100/007bff/ffffff?text=P3\" alt=\"Podcast 3 Cover\">\n                    <h3>Mindful Living</h3>\n                    <p>Tips and discussions for a balanced and healthier lifestyle.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/100/007bff/ffffff?text=P4\" alt=\"Podcast 4 Cover\">\n                    <h3>Creative Corner</h3>\n                    <p>Interviews with artists, writers, and creators.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;\">\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View All Podcasts</a>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Have questions, suggestions, or want to partner with us? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@podwave.net\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color); text-decoration: underline;\">info@podwave.net</a></p>\n            <p>Follow us on social media!</p>\n            <div style=\"margin-top: 15px;\">\n                <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color); text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;\">Facebook</a> |\n                <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color); text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;\">Twitter</a> |\n                <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color); text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;\">Instagram</a>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 PodWave Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple JS for smooth scrolling to section anchors\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}